<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n38016b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n38" href="#n38016b">N38 (VI.B.32)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n38all.htm#n38016b"> 16(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Palestine Day</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><b>&ldquo;<mark>Palestine Day</mark>&rdquo; in Bombay / Bombay, May 17</b> Palestine Day was observed by Moslems here yesterday. A huge procession paraded the Mohammedan quarters bearing slogans, such as &ldquo;Down with the Balfour Declaration&rdquo;, emblazoned on banners. The meeting in the evening was attended by 100,000 people. <br>A resolution was passed warning the British Government that &ldquo;if they do not take steps to satisfy Moslem claims in Palestine, Moslems will have to consider what steps they will take to bring pressure to compel the British Government to admit their rightful claims.&rdquo;&mdash;Reuter. <small> <a name="MP19may30" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#MP19may30"><cite title="source">Morning Post</cite></a> (19 May 1930) 13/6</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
